title: Germany's far-right AfD supporters outnumbered by protesters in Berlin
text:
Germany's far-right AfD supporters outnumbered by protesters in Berlin 12:47pm EDT - 00:52
Supporters of the far-right Alternative for Germany (AfD) marched through the streets of Berlin on Sunday. However, they were heavily outnumbered by anti-AfD demonstrators. Rough cut (no reporter narration) ▲ Hide Transcript ▶ View Transcript
